data.description: Immaculate New Construction. City living with Country feel. Huge 1ST floor Master Bedroom. Vaulted Ceiling in main living area. LVT in common areas and master bedroom/bathroom with carpet in other bedrooms.  Large Laundry room. Open Kitchen and living area. Spacious 2-Car garage. Metal balusters with oak treads on stairs.  Granite Countertops in kitchen with SS appliances. Large patio on rear for Grilling.  Rocking Chair front porch. New Park being Constructed across street.
